FBIS4-63474 "drsov099_f_94013" FBIS-SOV-94-099 Daily Report 20 May 1994 National Affairs Meshkov Asks Russia To Prevent Kiev Imposing Direct Rule Meshkov Asks Russia To Prevent Kiev Imposing Direct Rule LD2005212094 Moscow Radio Moscow in Russian to Tajikistan 1600 GMT 20 May 94 LD2005212094 Moscow Radio Moscow Russian BFN [From the "Slavyanka" program of the Russian Defense Ministry] [Text] Yuriy Meshkov, president of the Republic of Crimea, has called upon Russia to prevent Ukraine introducing direct presidential rule in Crimea. Speaking at a session of the local parliament, he pointed out that Ukraine is intensifying pressure on Crimea and is striving to provoke yet another conflict.
